  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0db6\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dda \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 1648\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "1648 crore for school books next year",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education states that it is expected that an amount of 1648 crore rupees will be spent to print school textbooks for the upcoming 2023 academic year.",
        "Accordingly, the Ministry says that about 45 percent of the school textbooks needed for the new academic year will be printed by the State Printing Legalized Corporation and the other 55 percent by private printers.",
        "The Ministry also says that raw paper for printing school textbooks will be imported under Indian loan assistance."
      ],
